{"tid":1560244,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"社會變革十大覺悟","createTime":"2019-09-11T06:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T06:46:41.000Z","uid":159293,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf6b92285ce46d6ee580f77824aefaedbf8ecce","tid":1560244,"uid":159293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:33:43.000Z","msg":"1.變革將會推翻既得利益者群體，他們會無所不用其極阻止你<br />\n2.單憑政治正當性及道理絕不能解決所有問題 <br />\n3.當政治正當性及道理失效，武力將會派上用場<br />\n4.武力亦無法百份百解決問題，盲目使用單一手段將會失衡 <br />\n5.知識及文化傳承是延續理想的唯一方法，公民覺醒將會有更多同路人<br />\n6.世上永遠有毫不作為或助紂為虐的人，說服他們毫無意義 <br />\n7.一子錯滿盤皆落索的情況下，別被情緒控制，報仇不急於一時<br />\n8.同路人的目的不一定跟你一致，有人為理想，亦有人為利益<br />\n9.推動變革的永遠是少眾，太多人不懂亦不願理解，他們只會冷眼旁觀<br />\n10.時刻反省，不要成為自己想推翻的極權"},{"pid":"5bd7e65a9e43e8179b48a6db9f1d6bc6a113be99","tid":1560244,"uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:35:30.000Z","msg":"全中"},{"pid":"00927c8251c986ee4a73f605f743622f8400ce51","tid":1560244,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"香港需要變革者"},{"pid":"96fc072cf1845cab441b60360ac838bddd87001d","tid":1560244,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00927c8251c986ee4a73f605f743622f8400ce51","tid":1560244,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"香港需要變革者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"變革定革命啊？唔同嫁喎。"},{"pid":"fd8bb7a1449548bf47b67135898eef8b5f89b653","tid":1560244,"uid":43204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:41:25.000Z","msg":"做乜唔post source ?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L6g4QOGqMBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL6g4QOGqMBY&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=5cf15988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L6g4QOGqMBY</a>"},{"pid":"dbba0ae19ee4c26a3cd2d6c4796ad047a0a4d7c1","tid":1560244,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl